### read all users
GET http://localhost:8074/user-api/user

### read a user by id
GET http://localhost:8074/user-api/user/301

### create a new user
POST http://localhost:8074/user-api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id":3013,
    "name":"mahi",
    "age":19
}

### update a user
PUT http://localhost:8074/user-api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id":301,
    "name":"mahesh",
    "age":22
}

### delete a user by id
DELETE http://localhost:8074/user-api/user/3013




### read all products
GET http://localhost:8074/product-api/product

### read all products by brand
GET http://localhost:8074/product-api/product/ht

###create new product
POST http://localhost:8074/product-api/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productid":301,
    "name":"laptop",
    "brand":"ht",
    "price":20000
}

### update a product
PUT http://localhost:8074/product-api/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "productid":301,
    "name":"laptop",
    "brand":"victus",
    "price":20000
}

### delete a product by id
DELETE http://localhost:8074/product-api/product/301

